name: CytochromeP4503A4Inhibitors
title: Cytochrome P450 3A4 inhibitors
description: RxNorm semantic clinical drug and semantic branded drug concepts for drugs that inhibit Cytochrome P450 3A4 (CYP3A4) as evidenced by changes of >= 2.0 in CYP3A4 probe substrates.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Drug-drug interaction clinical decision support),(Data Element Scope: RxNorm drugs),(Inclusion Criteria: RxNorm semantic clinical drug and semantic branded drug concepts for drugs that inhibit Cytochrome P450 3A4 (CYP3A4) as evidenced by changes of >= 2.0 in CYP3A4 probe substrates.),(Exclusion Criteria: Non-bioavailable dose forms e.g., shampoos and creams)
